properties.text: The once-beautiful city gates of Kinstown Harbor are now tarnished and crumbling. Will you enter the ruins?
Climb up to the cliffside village of Moorhaven?
Will you enter the Elvish town of Port Artha?
You stand at the entrance of the Goblin's Mountain Fortress. Horrific sights and smells await within, dare you enter?
You stand before Castle Bashgar, the capital of the Suvian Kingdom. Will you enter?
The sacred grounds of Ashvari have served as the burial grounds for the Suvian Kings for centuries. Dare you explore the Ashvari Crypts?
Through the swirling snow you perceive a large keep with tall, sheer walls coated in ice. Will you enter Rogaard Keep, last refuge of the Dwarves?
You stand before the mighty Vygurn Tower, a place of great mystery and intrigue. You are astonished to see that it is protected by no door, nor any guards. Step into Vygurn Tower?
On this island you find a bustling village, mostly occupied by merchants, sailors and buccaneers. Will you warily enter and peruse their wares?

properties.title: Blocked
properties.text: An enormous blockade prevents your passage!
At the base of Mount Vezu, you find an entrance to a cavern. A sulfurous odor wells up from within. Will you steel your nerves and enter?
You are set upon by vicious snakes!
